{"tid":2336738,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普將簽署行政令 讓聯邦建築重現古典風格","createTime":"2020-12-22T23:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T00:31:14.000Z","uid":176279,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"77ded99204943738e55d0770d69c856b1162cd96","tid":2336738,"uid":176279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:13:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/2/7/n11850654.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F2%2F7%2Fn11850654.htm&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpPiPq%2FHqG0pMUyXzarzxqBM%3D&h=375c88db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/2/7/n11850654.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n據《國會山》報導，知情者說，這份行政令將在下個月簽署，內容包括鼓勵聯邦建築呈現希臘和羅馬建築風格，而不是現代派建築風格。<br />\n<br />\n由《芝加哥太陽時報》公布的行政令草稿顯示，「古典和傳統建築風格被證明能夠激發人們對美國自治系統的肅然起敬。」<br />\n<br />\n國家公民藝術協會會長史密斯（Marion Smith）之前表示：「長期以來，（所謂）建築界精英和官僚們嘲笑帶有真正美感的元素，公然忽視公眾對優雅風格的看法，並悄悄的花費納稅人的錢，去建造醜陋、昂貴而低效的建築。」<br />\n<br />\n川普去年與意大利總統馬塔雷拉舉行聯合新聞會時說：「美國和意大利享有共同的文化和政治遺產，可追溯到幾千年前的古羅馬。」"},{"pid":"4504aca1e6f778131a22f059d423d1e73a639239","tid":2336738,"uid":176279,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Q0ppG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Q0ppG6.jpg&h=d6cb44d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4B4pG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4B4pG7.jpg&h=6247c191&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"044d2eb25397431fe1c3f906ee3d577f262f7e40","tid":2336738,"uid":176279,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:19:37.000Z","msg":"其實應該係 房屋台 開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開錯時事台"},{"pid":"605fd9961dbe9fd887c7e47baf36c87209c5cd74","tid":2336738,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T23:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj